(1) Initial Disclosures.
(a). Every promoter 21[, member of the promoter group] , key managerial personnel and director of every company whose securities are listed on any recognised stock exchange shall disclose his holding of securities of the company as on the date of these regulations taking effect, to the company within thirty days of these regulations taking effect;
(b). Every person on appointment as a key managerial personnel or a director of the company or upon becoming a 22[promoter or member of the promoter group] shall disclose his holding of securities of the company as on the date of appointment or becoming a promoter, to the company within seven days of such appointment or becoming a promoter.

